BT /F1 16 Tf 50 760 Td (Tallfind ? One-Page App Summary) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 736 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 720 Td (What it is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 704 Td (? Tallfind is a static web directory for finding tall-friendly clothing stores.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 688 Td (? It curates hand-reviewed entries for men and women, with verified sizing metadata.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 672 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 656 Td (Who it's for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 640 Td (? Primary persona: tall shoppers \(men ~6'2"+ and women ~5'9"+\) who struggle to find) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 624 Td (  reliable tall sizing across brands.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 608 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 592 Td (What it does) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 576 Td (? Loads separate men's and women's store datasets from local JSON files.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 560 Td (? Provides tabbed browsing \(Home, Men's, Women's\) with URL-synced filter state.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 544 Td (? Supports keyword search across store metadata \(name, sizing, notes, categories\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 528 Td (? Filters by tall-only brands, tops, bottoms, favorites, and men's minimum inseam.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 512 Td (? Offers sort modes \(tall-first, A?Z, and inseam for men's listings\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 496 Td (? Saves user favorites and analytics consent in localStorage.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 480 Td (? Collects store submissions and feedback via Formspree modal forms.) Tj ET
