BT /F1 10 Tf 50 432 Td (? Front end: `index.html` + `assets/styles.css` + `assets/app.js` rendered in-browser.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 416 Td (? Data layer: static JSON files \(`data/men.json`, `data/women.json`,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 400 Td (  `data/featured.json`\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 384 Td (? Runtime flow: browser fetches JSON -> JS stores state -> applies search/filter/sort ->) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 368 Td (  renders cards and homepage sections dynamically.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 352 Td (? Integrations: Google Analytics \(gtag with consent banner\), Formspree form endpoints.) Tj ET
